      *--------------*
      *
     C           @TYPE     IFNE *BLANK
     C           @ZAIS     ORNE *BLANK
     C           @ZAIK     ORNE 0
     C           @TYPE     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVELER,1      @ERR
     C                     SETON                     0399
