** @ERR
E-01 INPUT WIRE TYPE.
E-02 INPUT WIRE.
E-03 INPUT WIRE DIAMETER.
E-04 ORDER NO IS WRONG.
E-05 INPUT SUPPLIER.
E-06 SUPPLIER IS NOT FOUND IN DETAIL MGR M/F (SAIMOKU MASTER).
E-07 THIS PAGE IS DISPLAYED THE DATA OF BOTTOM PAGE.
E-08 THIS PAGE IS DISPLAYED THE DATA OF TOP PAGE.
E-09 NO DATA.
E-10 RENEW CODE IS WRONG.
E-11 INPUT INVOICE NO.
E-12 INPUT ORDER NO.
E-13 ORDER NO IS WRONG.
E-14 INPUT ITEM NO.
E-15 ITEM NO IS WRONG.
E-16 INPUT ITEM NO.
E-17 ITEM NO IS WRONG.
E-18 INPUT WIRE TYPE.
E-19 WIRE TYPE IS WRONG<'W' OR 'R'>.
E-20 INPUT WIRE.
E-21 INPUT WIRE DIAMETER.
E-22 DATA NOT FOUND IN WIRE KANBAN M/F.
E-23 DATA NOT FOUND IN ROD KANBAN M/F.
E-24 INPUT CASE NO.
E-25 CASE NO IS WRONG.
E-26 DATA NOT FOUND IN MATERIAL ACCUOUNTS AGGREGATION DATA FILE.
E-27 SAME DATA IS ALREADY ENTERED.
E-28 INPUT ORDER DATE.
E-29 ORDER DATE IS WRONG.
E-30 INPUT DEPARTURE JP PORT DATE.
E-31 DEPARTURE JP PORT DATE IS WRONG.
E-32 INPUT RECIEPT DATE.
E-33 RECIEPT DATE IS WRONG.
E-34 INPUT PAYMENT DATE.
E-35 PAYMENT DATE IS WRONG.
E-36 INPUT TRANSPORTATION.
E-37 TRANSPORTATION IS WRONG.
E-38 INPUT WEIGHT.
E-39 INPUT UNIT PRICE.
E-40 PRICE CODE IS WRONG<'YEN' OR 'US '>.
E-41 WIRE TYPE IS WRONG<'W' OR 'R'>.
